name: Agent Anna
overview: Agent Anna is a New Zealand Comedy-drama television series, created by Maxine Fleming with Vanessa Alexander and devised by Robyn Malcolm. Produced by Great Southern Film and Television and funded by NZ On Air and Television New Zealand. It began airing its first series of six episodes in New Zealand on 31 January 2013. It was confirmed on 12 August 2013 that the show had been renewed for a second series of 10 episodes.

episodes.name: Agent Anna
episodes.overview: Robyn Malcolm stars as Anna, a down-on-her-luck single mum who has no other choice, but to sell real estate for a living.

episodes.name: Swimming with Sharks
episodes.overview: Desperate for money, Anna decides to put her moral principles aside and feign friendship with a dead woman in order to get a sale.

episodes.name: Happiness
episodes.overview: Struggling to deal with her own marriage ending, Anna now has the nightmare of a depressed vendor who cannot get over his wife leaving with the dog.

episodes.name: At Home Here
episodes.overview: Determined to be more assertive, Anna ignores Leon's advice and decides to market her new property only to new immigrants and Polynesians.

episodes.name: Rules of the World
episodes.overview: On the verge of losing her job, Anna is saved by her boss who seems overly keen to take her to a real estate conference in Tauranga for the weekend.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Change is afoot in Anna's world. The Auckland inner city housing market is booming. Suddenly there is excitement in the office. Will things start to happen for Anna?

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: An agent with no listings makes no money, so Anna goes in search of houses to sell and finds a lot more than she bargained for.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: As she hesitates to take a huge risk, Anna gets an unexpected makeover and makes a bold decision.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Anna jumps on the property ladder, but finds the rungs are slippery and the stakes are high - has she got what it takes?

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Juggling with high finance and a mad mother, Anna makes a tough choice and an unexpected discovery.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: A family gathering opens old wounds and reveals new possibilities for Anna.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: When Anna is nominated for an award, her big night brings surprises, revelations and a very strange encounter.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Newly fired up for success, Anna re-negotiates an old relationship and makes a new deal.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Her ex-husband wants to make peace, but Anna's ready for war - who wins and who goes down?

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Things are looking up for Anna in tonight's season finale, but for just how long will they stay that way?
